metadata.name: Face it
metadata.description:
First work in the Black and White collection. This work is a freely distributed Open Edition and will be used to provide access to the other works in the collection.

This is an ERC-1155 open edition minted on a manifold smart contract.

More information and the history of the collection at  
https://reiniscouple.space
